<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; visibility: visible;">各位已录取我校的同学们:</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.25em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; visibility: visible;">感谢您选择江西软件职业技术大学。我校已经按照教育厅录取相关规定，完成了录取手续的办理，欢迎加入江西软件职业技术大学大家庭。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2.25em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; visibility: visible;">学校为了统一管理，单招录取与统招录取考生享受相同的待遇与服务，经学校招生委员会综合考虑，我校单招录取考生通知书的发放时间将与统招专科录取考生同步发放，请大家耐心等候，如有特殊需求，请致电0791-83792888，我们将竭诚为您提供相关服务！谢谢大家的支持！</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 0em; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">江西软件职业技术大学招生录取办公室</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-indent: 0em; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">2024年5月9日</span></p>